  <T n="entry_text">0x65655D8B<!--String: "The Lost Adventurer"--></T>
  <V n="entry_text_description" t="enabled">
    <T n="enabled">0x704757D0<!--String: "The Lost Adventurer is renowned for his dedication to exploring new worlds and uncovering mysteries. Inspired by his childhood adventures, and once part of a group called The Great Adventurers, Raheel has spent his adult life traveling to distant places. Though rarely seen since his initial departure, it is said he occasionally returns home. His sibling, Laxmi, only sees him sporadically and never quite knows his current whereabouts or when he will return. With a twinkle in his eye and a heart full of wonder, The Lost Adventurer weaves stories of enchantment wherever he roams, leaving behind a trail of awe and curiosity."--></T>
